            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>For the safety of Imperator Caesar Titus Aelius Hadrianus Antoninus Augustus Pius, father of the fatherland and Marcus Allus [Aelius?] Aurelius, our Caesar, to the Genius of the colony of Puteoli. Chrysanthus, dispensator of Augustus for the grain in Puteoli and Ostia. This place was given with the permission of the decurions.</p>
